A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Code Section 16-6-22 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to
2 incest, so as to include step-grandparent and step-grandchild relationship; to provide for
3 related matters; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
4 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
5 SECTION 1.
6 Code Section 16-6-22 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to incest, is
7 amended by revising paragraph (4) of subsection (a) as follows:
8 "(4) Grandparent and grandchild of the whole blood or of the half blood or
9 step-grandparent and step-grandchild;"
10 SECTION 2.
11 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
